  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC441">
        <l>colle ṉecca muṉṉum piṉṉuñ</l>
	<l>collaḷa valla teñcuta lilavē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/245/mode/1up">245</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/245/mode/1up">245</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, colleccattiṟku muṭipu kūṟutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : colleṉeccam muṉṉāyiṉum piṉṉāyiṉum colleṉṉuñ coṟkoṇṭu muṭitalallatu piṟitillai eṉṟavāṟu</p>
<p>varalāṟu: 'pacittēṉ paḻañcōṟu tā eṉa niṉṟāḷ' eṉpatām.</p>
<p>maṟṟut tā eṉa niṉṟāḷ piṟaḷēyeṉiṉ, tā eṉac colliniṉṟāḷ eṉpatām. avaṟṟuṭ colli eṉṟāṉum colla eṉṟāṉum āka, iraṇṭaṉuḷ oṉṟaṉāṉ muṭiyum atu eṉpatu.</p>
<p>'muṉṉum' eṉṟatu, tā eṉac colli niṉṟāḷ eṉṟu koṇarntu muṭippiṉ, atu piṉ muṭivupaṭa niṉṟatām eṉpatu.		(45)</p> </body>
  </text>

